<XMLDocContent PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetConsole.CloseConsoleHandle" Title="CloseConsoleHandle method" xmlns="http://www.cobaltrenderer.com/schema/XMLDocSchema.xsd">
  <Paragraph>
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.Welcome">Home</PageRef> ->
    <PageRef PageName="cobalt.logging.LogTargetConsole">LogTargetConsole</PageRef> ->
    CloseConsoleHandle
  </Paragraph>
  <Section Title="Description">
    <Paragraph>
      The <TypeRef>CloseConsoleHandle</TypeRef> method closes the current console handle if one is open.
    </Paragraph>
    <Note Type="Important">
      <Paragraph>
        Calling this method when no console handle is open has no effect.
      </Paragraph>
    </Note>
  </Section>
  <Section Title="Usage">
    <Code Language="C++"><![CDATA[void CloseConsoleHandle();]]></Code>
  </Section>
